@startuml
actor Admin
participant "Browser" as Browser
participant "CategoryAdminController" as Controller
participant "CategoryService" as Service
participant "CategoryRepository" as Repo
participant "AuditService" as Audit

Admin -> Browser: Click edit icon
Browser -> Controller: GET /admin/api/categories/edit/{id}
activate Controller
Controller -> Service: getById(id)
Service -> Repo: findById(id)
Repo --> Service: oldCategory
Service --> Controller: oldCategory
deactivate Controller
Controller --> Browser: JSON (oldCategory)
Browser -> Browser: Hiển thị modal với dữ liệu cũ
Admin -> Browser: Sửa tên, trạng thái, Submit
Browser -> Controller: POST /admin/api/categories/save (form data)
activate Controller
Controller -> Service: getById(id) (lấy oldValue)
Service -> Repo: findById(id)
Repo --> Service: oldCategory
Service --> Controller: oldCategory
Controller -> Service: save(updatedCategory)
activate Service
Service -> Repo: save(updatedCategory)
Repo --> Service: saved
Service --> Controller: done
deactivate Service
Controller -> Audit: log(user, "UPDATE", "Category", id, oldCategory, updatedCategory)
Audit -> DB: INSERT audit_logs
Controller --> Browser: ResponseEntity.ok("success")
deactivate Controller
Browser -> Browser: Đóng modal, tải lại danh sách
@enduml